data.title: Jane Wyman Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Jane Wyman on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Jane Wyman including My Man Godfrey, Pollyanna, and more.
data.text:
Who Is Sylvia?

Steve's (Fred MacMurray) old girlfriend, now a rich divorcee, comes to town and gives Barbara (Beverly Garland) a few jealous moments.

The Doctor Willoughby Story

A female doctor is traveling west - and Indians threaten to attack the train unless the doctor can save a badly injured chief.

Wagon Train Mutiny

The wagon train comes across a devastated wagon party where they find Renaldo, a wounded member of the attacking comancheros who was left to die by his comrades.
